prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D artwork for a birthday card front cover for Sarah, humorous and lighthearted. A dreamy fantasy anime style illustration of two characters based on reference photo 0fd8568f-bfef-4339-af35-193c5d8c3123. The two people are transformed into whimsical, enchanting fairy-tale versions of themselves, maintaining their exact hairstyles, facial features, body proportions, and relative positions. They are wearing the same clothing as in the photo, but with any logos or text omitted. The characters are depicted stumbling comically into a magical, enchanted forest filled with oversized, glowing mushrooms, sparkling flora, and mischievous, tiny floating fairies. Their expressions are ones of funny surprise and slight bewilderment. The atmosphere is magical and whimsical, with soft pastel colors, ethereal light beams filtering through a canopy of shimmering leaves, and detailed, enchanting nature elements. In the center area, the text "Happy Birthday, Sarah! Welcome to the senior discount section of the enchanted forest." is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall style is soft, detailed, and has a whimsical, fairy-tale quality.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
